{"tid":1811233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果廣告製作公司（11） - 重要支線任務","createTime":"2020-01-04T13:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T20:35:26.000Z","uid":81385,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0b85298e030798fe042732cd778219aa60738f74","tid":1811233,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"相信大家唔會唔記得上年呢個時候<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Hg4dc6a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHg4dc6a.gif&h=1580e5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後將連登仔分裂成兩派<br />\n一派認為同2003年呢蘋果廣告有關，以及及後23條立法，50萬人上街，沙士有關<br />\n<br />\n另一派人就持相反意見<br />\n其後cctvb求其貼張A4紙平息風波<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/havH1Sd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhavH1Sd.png&h=7b71c848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人意見: 我唔係話一個廣告就可以導致咁多野重現，但係必須正視係咪背後有人搞局<br />\n而如果查到背後有人 1) 推動送中 及其他殘害香港人行為 ; 2) 以新病毒做生化武器打壓異己<br />\n而大家都估到係邊個做<br />\n咁對國際/美國戰線好有用<br />\n尤其 2) 係危害國際安全，2003年沙士美國都有人死<br />\n<br />\n所以調查目標唔係停留係個廣告表面，而係一年前到依家背後鮮為人知嘅事件<br />\n希望手足可以團結番一齊，得閒做後援戰線時跟下呢條線"},{"pid":"66f0658bf514ad44136674521b2cf4f4ae4c207f","tid":1811233,"uid":68728,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"而家又有新沙士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f91af79cf40641661dfd0bce1aa8f35db65e17","tid":1811233,"uid":81385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66f0658bf514ad44136674521b2cf4f4ae4c207f","tid":1811233,"uid":68728,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"而家又有新沙士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"要跟下係咪早有預謀攻香港"},{"pid":"b707db54bba3b33be720bf3eb0cd1ce697477314","tid":1811233,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"